-sm font-semibold text-navy-deep dark:text-slate-200\">Пароль</label>\n<a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"#\">Забыли пароль?</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative group\">\n<input class=\"w-full h-12 px-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 text-navy-deep dark:text-white placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" placeholder=\"••••••••\" type=\"password\"/>\n<button class=\"absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400 hover:text-navy-deep dark:hover:text-white\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]\">visibility</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Remember Me -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 py-1\">\n<input class=\"w-4 h-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"remember\" type=\"checkbox\"/>\n<label class=\"text-sm text-slate-muted dark:text-slate-400\" for=\"remember\">Запомнить меня</label>\n</div>\n<!-- Action Button -->\n<button class=\"w-full h-12 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-md shadow-primary/20\" type=\"submit\">\n                    Войти\n                </button>\n</form>\n<!-- Social Login Divider -->\n<div class=\"relative my-8\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center\">\n<div class=\"w-full border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative flex justify-center text-xs uppercase\">\n<span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-navy-deep px-2 text-slate-muted\">Или продолжить с</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Social Buttons -->\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<button class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 h-11 px-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors\">\n<img alt=\"G\" class=\"size-5\" data-alt=\"Google colorful brand logo icon\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCx9NAKDGX5mWY0I3GWvZQy_Xkrgg1PMES-m7nyE-nlVmPyYFwIae3QeQ357A-f3jPEnWndg_NJV5hXmCqHIuwV89Zk3RnNtoZguauqUW8QMJmzsmSRGf4UcIDuKbblO3gdMI3ibU-6byxnN76QAnlf4QySohc2FChPvvZe60y2Rvqkfm6xEfBRB0CGUCCXCkFHJX8zJj4Yx8BNFOTKZKjESKc8YrEiWJzHJnJTnqftdSlUP7R2skDN4HURgginOP1HgIICrX3CCg_s\"/>\n<span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-navy-deep dark:text-white\">Google</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 h-11 px-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors\">\n<img alt=\"VK\" class=\"size-5\" data-alt=\"VK Russian social network logo icon\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDjj802BJqCVZIhTC8vqiIURViwgBAYXQF9vBq1pfiEukbN1hYVwqh7x8Xmq2ynMwX0BBURv3XlcBP8CnRIpvrL7QXMgIg6qOdPTeIDH5LN_tVphDBSYup5pQg8VFe2xtX1IY62ukz9eMy6zKUyu25_QiwFDOuhrvwJp8rM1Bq0VxxC0xPuc1SLtbMe1HV2km4MSLtG0LHPrK_xR8Ac6o3F6MOv4F_CVf77ElJ-4LfGspIrC_fkNtxku1nMCNP8ESKebTHNVQNTSg0x\"/>\n<span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-navy-deep dark:text-white\">ВКонтакте</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n<!-- Footer Link -->\n<div class=\"mt-8 text-center\">\n<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-muted dark:text-slate-400\">\n                    Нет аккаунта? \n                    <a class=\"text-primary font-bold hover:underline\" href=\"#\">Создать аккаунт</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- System Status Info -->\n<div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center gap-6 text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n<span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n<span class=\"size-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\"></span>\n                Система онлайн\n            </span>\n<span>Версия 2.4.0</span>\n<a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Поддержка</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body></html>"}
